name: Nana
review: I use it to apply my Revlon liquid foundation as well as blending out under eye concealer. It works very well

name: Wild Llama
review: Used it for foundation and anti redness creme and it worked well for me.

name: Pinky
review: Not too bad, easy to use, ergonomic.  Would make the sponge a tad bigger, but liquid makeup went on smoothly and streak free.

name: Makeup Gal
review: This was NOT what I was expecting. It left my makeup very streaking & sucked up a lot of my product.
